dino-im (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release v0.2 - Read Receipts Feature
    - Add visible read receipt indicators for all sent messages
    - Show different icons for sending, sent, delivered, read, and error states
    - Indicators are always visible (not just in message headers)
    - Real-time updates as message status changes
    - Works with merged/consecutive messages
    - Full XEP-0333 Chat Markers support

  * Previous release v0.1 - Text Zoom Feature
    - Add AI-generated text zoom feature (Ctrl++, Ctrl+-, Ctrl+0)
    - Add resizable sidebar
    - Full UI scaling for all elements

